Type <code>object</code> Required Yes Additional properties Any type allowed <p>Description: In accordance with pve qm cli tool, creation parameters mapped (key equals the --key part and value the passed value).</p> <p>Example:</p> <pre><code>{
    "cores": 1,
    "memory": 1024
}
</code></pre>

